summary: This is a travel authorization email from the DOJ's E2 travel system, approving a trip to Stockholm, Sweden from February 3-6, 2020 for the purpose of conducting witness interviews related to the Epstein investigation (case reference 2018R01618). The authorization is pending further approval.

events.title: Planned Witness Interviews in Stockholm
events.description: A DOJ investigator or prosecutor is scheduled to travel to Stockholm, Sweden to conduct witness interviews for the Epstein investigation.
